  "html": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91); font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;\">The focus of this repetition is on these sentences:</span></p><div class=\"fr-view\"><p>Sentence 1 - まにあうかな。= I wonder if we will make it.</p><p>Sentence 2 - おいしいかな。= I wonder if it&#39;s good.</p><p><strong>How to use this lesson</strong> - When the repeat message shows and the video pauses, please repeat the sentence you have just heard. Keep practising until you can repeat perfectly!</p><p><span class=\"fr-video fr-fvc fr-dvb\"><iframe src=\"https://platform.thinkific.com/videoproxy/v1/play/bsf60v19tnhu54jnj5q0\" scrolling=\"no\" class=\"videoproxy_embed\" title=\"D57 L3 R1.mp4 - 00:07\" name=\"videoproxy_embed\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></span><br></p></div>",
